dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.enterprise.wf.wres.WorkforceOrganizationRole
dataStructure.description:
This is a PartyRole that represents organizations involved in field operations. It can be the CSP Field Technician department itself, or a 3rd-party contractor company. Note that OrganizationRole has Calendar, inherited from Calendar of PartyRole.

This entity is optional
